PL 20/02/2014
Updated: HM 11/08/2020

FLRWSolver -- supplying cosmological initial conditions for the ET

Directions:
	* Put the entire thorn (i.e., the folder FLRWSolver) in the directory Cactus/arrangements/EinsteinInitialData/
          You can do this directly from the git repository on bitbucket using:
          
          cd Cactus/arrangements/EinsteinInitialData/
          git clone https://USERNAME@bitbucket.org/hayleymac/flrwsolver.git
          
          replacing USERNAME with your bitbucket username.

	* Add a line in the thornlist (Cactus/manifest/einsteintoolkit.th) below other EinsteinInitialData thorns:
	      EinsteinInitialData/flrwSolver

	* Compile (see README.Compilation for details)
    
    * See the documentation for detailed instructions on choosing perturbations and other parameters
    
    * Enjoy!
